Network Topology Overview

client-vm (Workstation)
 Subnet: 192.168.10.0/24
 IP: 192.168.10.10
 Gateway: 192.168.10.1

router-vm (3 NIC Router)
 eth0 (client-net): 192.168.10.1
 eth1 (server-net): 192.168.20.1
 eth2 (router-net): 192.168.99.1
 Performs routing between the two subnets and provides NAT.

srv-web (Web Server)
 Subnet: 192.168.20.0/24
 IP: 192.168.20.10
 Gateway: 192.168.20.1
